/**
 * ============================================================
 * Project Framework Summary – Aerosimple Mobile Automation
 * ============================================================
 *
 * Project Name:
 *  - Aerosimple Mobile App Regression Automation
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Programming Language
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - JavaScript (ES6 / ES Modules)
 *  - async / await syntax
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Automation Framework
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - WebdriverIO (WDIO v9)
 *    • Used as test runner
 *    • Manages sessions, execution, reporting
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Mobile Automation Tool
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - Appium 2
 *  - Android automation backend: UiAutomator2
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Test Framework
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - Mocha (BDD style)
 *    • describe()
 *    • it()
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Design Pattern
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - Page Object Model (POM)
 *    • Test logic separated from UI interaction logic
 *    • Improves maintainability and reusability
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Platform & Device
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - Android platform
 *  - Android Emulator
 *  - Device connection via ADB
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Application Type
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - Hybrid Mobile Application
 *    • Native container
 *    • WebView support (to be automated next)
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Configuration Management
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - wdio.conf.js
 *    • Desired capabilities
 *    • App package & activity
 *    • Timeouts
 *    • Runner configuration
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Dependency Management
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - Node.js
 *  - npm
 *  - package.json
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Test Execution
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - Command:
 *      npm run wdio
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Reporting
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - WDIO Spec Reporter
 *    • Console-based execution results
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Key Technical Concepts Used
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  - Desired Capabilities
 *  - Appium Session Lifecycle
 *  - noReset strategy
 *  - Emulator-based execution
 *  - Capability-based app launching
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Project Structure
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  Aerosimple_MobileApp_Regression
 *   ├── package.json
 *   ├── wdio.conf.js
 *   └── test
 *       ├── specs
 *       │   └── login.js
 *       └── pageobjects
 *           └── login.page.js
 *
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Interview Summary (One Line)
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
 *  "Built a mobile automation framework using JavaScript,
 *   WebdriverIO, and Appium for Android following the
 *   Page Object Model with Mocha test framework."
 *
 * ============================================================
